NAME
    meon::Web2 - flexible file-based web content management system

SYNOPSYS
        $ plackup -Ilib --port 8089 --server Twiggy bin/meon-Web2.psgi
        $ curl http://localhost:8089/

DESCRIPTION
    This is an early successor of meon::Web build to run using async Twiggy
    for speed and elegance.

SEE ALSO
    meon::Web2::Req - request-respond class

